				<div class="dablink">This article is about the group of Northern and Southwestern Chinese dialects.  For the official spoken standardized Chinese language (Putonghua/Guoyu), see <a href="/wiki/Standard_Chinese" title="Standard Chinese">Standard Chinese</a>.</div>
